headline.main: Determined Rodriguez Out to Prove His Real Madrid Credentials
headline.print_headline: Determined Rodriguez Out to Prove His Real Madrid Credentials

lead_paragraph: James Rodriguez has struggled to find a place in Real Madrid under Zinedine Zidane, but he has not given up hope of forcing his way in.
